2026-05-10T05:16:17.6249612Z 12    <!--
2026-05-10T05:16:17.6249998Z 13        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-10T05:16:17.6250338Z 14        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-10T05:16:17.6251275Z 15        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-10T05:16:17.6251679Z 16        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-10T05:16:17.6252155Z 17        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
